headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Bikers Snapmatic Contest
content:
Get ready to put your best shots forward in our #BIKERS Snapmatic photo challenge. We're on the search for five winning Snapmatics that showcase all the hottest features of Bikers, from the latest vehicles to Clubhouses going about their daily business. The five winners will not only get their Snapmatics featured on the Rockstar Newswire, but will also snap up GTA$1,000,000. Entry is open until Oct 10 and must be tagged with #BIKERS on Social Club.

Visit the Social Club for official rules.
